## 📊 Executive Summary

### System Overview

The IGOChain Purchase Module manages end-to-end procurement operations across two parallel workflows:

1. **Integrated Material Procurement** (Primary) - BOQ-driven workflow with multi-vendor quote comparison
2. **Standalone Purchase Orders** (Secondary) - Direct PO issuance with external vendor portal access

### Key Metrics & Capabilities

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| **Database Tables** | 5 core tables + 2 logging tables |
| **User Roles** | 7 (Employee, Purchase, BOI, Admin, CEO, GM, Accounts) |
| **Approval Levels** | 3-tier (BOI → Admin → CEO) |
| **Quote Comparison** | Minimum 3 quotes recommended |
| **Real-time Updates** | Supabase Realtime subscriptions |

### Business Impact

- **Transparency**: Complete audit trail from request to delivery
- **Cost Optimization**: Multi-quote comparison ensures best pricing
- **Efficiency**: Automated approval chains reduce processing time
- **Compliance**: Document integrity and BOI verification mandatory

