## 👥 User Workflows

### Workflow 1: Integrated Material Procurement (Primary)

#### Actor Roles & Responsibilities

| Role | Responsibilities | Key Actions |
|------|------------------|-------------|
| **Engineer/Site Team** | Identify material needs | Create request from BOQ |
| **Purchase Team** | Vendor sourcing & negotiation | Add 3+ quotes, track delivery |
| **BOI** | Quality & price verification | Audit quotes, approve/reject |
| **Admin** | Financial oversight | Approve high-value requests |
| **CEO** | Final authority | Approve critical/high-value items |
| **Accounts** | Payment execution | Process approved payments |

#### Complete Workflow Diagram

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant E as Engineer
    participant P as Purchase
    participant B as BOI
    participant A as Admin
    participant C as CEO
    participant AC as Accounts
    participant V as Vendor
    
    E->>P: Create Material Request
    Note over E: Select BOQ items + urgency
    
    P->>P: Start Sourcing
    P->>V: Contact Vendors
    V->>P: Quote 1
    V->>P: Quote 2
    V->>P: Quote 3
    
    P->>P: Select Best Quote
    P->>B: Submit for BOI Approval
    
    B->>B: Verify Rates & Specs
    alt BOI Approves
        B->>A: Forward to Admin
        A->>A: Financial Check
        alt Admin Approves
            A->>C: Forward to CEO
            C->>C: Final Review
            alt CEO Approves
                C->>AC: Auto-create Payment Request
                AC->>V: Execute Payment
                V->>E: Dispatch Material
                E->>E: Mark Delivered
            else CEO Holds
                C->>P: Request Clarification
            end
        else Admin Rejects
            A->>E: Rejection Notification
        end
    else BOI Rejects
        B->>P: Send Back for Rework
    end
```

#### Detailed Steps

##### Step 1: Engineer Creates Request

```typescript
// UI: Material Request Form
const createRequest = async () => {
  await useMaterialRequests().createRequest({
    project_id: selectedProject.id,
    phase_id: selectedPhase?.id,
    boq_items: [
      {
        boq_id: "uuid-1",
        material_name: "Cement (OPC 53)",
        quantity: 500,
        unit: "bags",
        estimated_rate: 450,
        total_estimated: 225000,
        urgent: true
      }
    ],
    urgency: "high",
    notes: "Required for foundation work - Phase 2"
  });
};
```

##### Step 2: Purchase Team Sourcing

```typescript
// UI: Purchase Dashboard - Sourcing Tab
const handleStartSourcing = async (requestId: string) => {
  // Update status to 'sourcing'
  await useMaterialRequests().updateRequest(requestId, {
    status: 'sourcing',
    assigned_to_purchase: user.id
  });
  
  // Add initial progress log
  await usePurchaseProgress().addProgress(
    requestId,
    "Started vendor sourcing process",
    "sourcing"
  );
};
```

##### Step 3: Add Vendor Quotes (Minimum 3)

```typescript
// UI: Add Quote Form
const addVendorQuote = async () => {
  await useVendorQuotes().addQuote({
    material_request_id: requestId,
    project_id: projectId,
    vendor_name: "ABC Cement Traders",
    vendor_contact: "+91 98765 43210",
    vendor_email: "sales@abccement.com",
    vendor_bank_name: "HDFC Bank",
    vendor_account_number: "50100123456789",
    vendor_ifsc: "HDFC0001234",
    vendor_gst: "27AABCU9603R1ZM",
    quoted_unit_price: 445,
    quoted_total: 222500,
    quoted_items: [
      {
        material_name: "Cement (OPC 53)",
        quantity: 500,
        unit: "bags",
        unit_price: 445,
        total: 222500
      }
    ],
    quote_drive_link: "https://drive.google.com/...",
    validity_date: "2026-03-06",
    delivery_days: 3,
    notes: "Bulk discount applied"
  });
};
```

##### Step 4: Quote Selection & Approval Initiation

```typescript
// UI: Quote Comparison Modal
const selectQuote = async (quoteId: string) => {
  // Selects quote & triggers BOI approval
  await useVendorQuotes().selectQuote(quoteId, requestId);
  // Auto-updates material_request.approval_status to 'pending_boi'
};
```

##### Step 5: BOI Approval

```typescript
// UI: BOI Orders Page
const approveAsBOI = async (requestId: string) => {
  await useMaterialRequests().approveRequest(requestId, 'boi');
  // Updates approval_status to 'boi_approved' → 'pending_admin'
};
```

##### Step 6: Admin Approval

```typescript
// UI: Admin Dashboard - Approvals Tab
const approveAsAdmin = async (requestId: string) => {
  await useMaterialRequests().approveRequest(requestId, 'admin');
  // Updates approval_status to 'admin_approved' → 'pending_ceo'
};
```

##### Step 7: CEO Final Approval & Auto-Payment

```typescript
// UI: CEO Dashboard - Approvals Tab
const approveAsCEO = async (requestId: string) => {
  await useMaterialRequests().approveRequest(requestId, 'ceo');
  
  // Auto-creates payment request in payment_requests table
  // Links payment to material_request via linked_payment_id
  
  // Notification sent to Accounts team
};
```

##### Step 8: Delivery Tracking

```typescript
// UI: Purchase Dashboard - Order Tracking
const updateDelivery = async (status: string) => {
  await useMaterialRequests().updateDeliveryStatus(
    requestId,
    status,  // 'ordered' → 'loading' → 'shipped' → 'unloading' → 'delivered'
    "LR #12345 - ABC Logistics - ETA: Feb 8, 2026"
  );
};
```

