### Workflow 2: Standalone Purchase Orders (Secondary)

#### Use Cases

- Quick procurement outside BOQ scope
- Service contracts
- Miscellaneous purchases
- Emergency orders

#### Workflow Diagram

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Employee: Create PO] --> B[Admin: Review]
    B --> C{Decision}
    C -->|Approve| D[CEO: Final Review]
    C -->|Reject| A
    D --> E{Decision}
    E -->|Approve| F[Payment Created]
    E -->|Hold| G[Request Clarification]
    E -->|Reject| A
    G --> D
```

#### Step-by-Step Process

##### Step 1: Create Purchase Order

```typescript
// UI: Purchase Order Form
const createPO = async () => {
  const result = await usePurchaseOrders().createPurchaseOrder({
    projectId: selectedProject.id,
    vendorName: "XYZ Suppliers Pvt Ltd",
    vendorBankDetails: "ICICI Bank - A/C: 123456789 - IFSC: ICIC0001234",
    vendorUpi: "xyz@icici",
    itemDescription: "Construction Tools - 50 items",
    quantity: 50,
    unitPrice: 1200,
    totalAmount: 60000,
    costComparisonUrl: "https://drive.google.com/file/...",
    poDocumentUrl: "https://drive.google.com/file/..."
  });
  
  // Auto-generates po_number via database sequence
  // Returns: { success: true, data: { po_number: 1234, ... } }
};
```

##### Step 2: Admin Approval

```typescript
const approveAsAdmin = async (poId: string) => {
  await usePurchaseOrders().approvePurchaseOrder(poId, 'admin');
  // status: 'pending' → 'admin_approved'
};
```

##### Step 3: CEO Approval

```typescript
const approveAsCEO = async (poId: string) => {
  await usePurchaseOrders().approvePurchaseOrder(poId, 'ceo');
  // status: 'admin_approved' → 'ceo_approved'
  // Triggers payment request creation (similar to material requests)
};
```

##### Step 4: Rejection/Hold Flows

```typescript
// Rejection
const rejectPO = async (poId: string) => {
  await usePurchaseOrders().rejectPurchaseOrder(
    poId,
    "Quote not competitive - please re-negotiate"
  );
  // status → 'rejected'
  // Requester can resubmit with updates
};

// Hold (CEO only)
const holdPO = async (poId: string) => {
  await usePurchaseOrders().holdPurchaseOrder(
    poId,
    "Waiting for budget approval from Board"
  );
  // status → 'ceo_hold'
};
```

##### Step 5: Resubmission

```typescript
const resubmitPO = async (poId: string) => {
  await usePurchaseOrders().resubmitPurchaseOrder(poId, {
    vendorName: "Better Vendor Ltd",
    totalAmount: 55000,  // Revised amount
    costComparisonUrl: "https://drive.google.com/new-comparison"
  });
  // Resets all approvals, status → 'pending'
};
```

